messages.message: Hey, yes — some of the PDF service interfaces are still in use (even though the service itself was removed). Even a year after we deprecated the PDF service, some customers continued deploying and using it from older bundles, which is why it wasn’t fully removed. Once those customers eventually upgraded, we just never got around to cleaning it up :man-facepalming:. Is this conversation still ongoing?
Yes we still need someone to implement this cleanup (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C06FA6A23/p1757464237772009?thread_ts=1757387419.073409&channel=C06FA6A23&message_ts=1757464237.772009)
